{
  "id": "adv_main_03_05_02",
  "title": "BIG4編1章22話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんとゆっくり話すのって\nちょっとだけ久しぶりかも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like it’s been a while since\nKotono-chan and I had a proper chat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1290100776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。最近はBIG4チャレンジに向けた\nレッスンで忙しかったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. Lately‚ we’ve been busy with\nlessons for the BIG4 Challenge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5951048303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、毎日晩御飯を食べる時に\nおねむさんだったもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone was sleepy\nat dinner every day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "沙季がぼーっとして、すずに向かって\n「千紗、これ食べる？」なんて言ったこともあったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki was spacing out and said to Suzu‚\n\"Chisa‚ do you want to eat this?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4680045128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！　沙季ちゃんてば、ハッとして\n顔が真っ赤になっちゃって。可愛かったな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah yeah! Saki-chan‚ she gasped\nand her face turned bright red. It was so cute~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5404001661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "……それで、どんなお話なのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ what did you want to talk about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6430386861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……渚。私……月ストを脱退して\n一人で頑張りたいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Nagisa. I… I want to withdraw from Moon Tempest\nand work hard on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 42.0413616498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.0413616498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんには伝えて\n今返事を待ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told {user}-san and\nI’m waiting for his answer now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3405992866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、{user}さんがどう\n動いてくれたとしても、この気持ちはもう変わらない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But no matter what {user}-san\ndoes‚ my feelings won’t change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5364639799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、どうして……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ why…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8364639799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "渚、私達……ずっと一緒に頑張ってきたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ we… We’ve been working hard together‚ haven’t we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2877112031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "うん。デビューしてから……ううん、その前からずっと\n私達五人で頑張ってきたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Ever since our debut… No‚ even before that‚\nthe five of us have been working hard together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.4883456483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "うまくいかなかったことだってあったよね\nあれだけ頑張ってもスリクスに負けて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were times when things didn’t go well.\nWe worked so hard‚ but we lost to IIIX…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "それでも……私達、心が折れそうになっても\nずっと、五人で、頑張って……きたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But still… even when we felt like giving up‚\nwe kept going… together‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3708004169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "うん、私もそう思う\nだけど……それでも、どりきゅんには勝てなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I think so too.\nBut… even so‚ we couldn’t beat DoriKyun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3336524607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 94.4336524607
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4336524607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "渚だって感じたでしょ？　あの時の圧倒的な差を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You felt it too‚ didn’t you‚ Nagisa? That overwhelming difference.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.2259200296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "もう少し練習すれば、もう少しうまくなれば\n手が届く……そんな差じゃなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we practiced a little more‚ if we got a little better‚\nwe could catch up… It wasn’t that kind of difference.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.0229098649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "うん、分かるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0925866963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "何を意識して、どれだけ頑張ったらあんな\nパフォーマンスが出来るのか、想像もつかなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn’t even imagine what we had to focus on or how hard\nwe had to work to be able to perform like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2826468826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "だから、どうしたらいいかずっと考えてた\n今のまま頑張っても、必ず行き詰まる時がくる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I’ve been thinking about what to do.\nIf we keep working hard the way we are now‚ there will definitely come a time",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3563548129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、きっともう……私達は壁に当たってる\nそれも、凄く凄く高い壁に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "when we hit a wall. No‚ I’m sure we’ve… already hit a wall.\nAnd it’s a very‚ very high wall.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0230214795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "だから……月ストを抜けるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… you’re leaving Moon Tempest?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.5230214795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "うん。沢山……沢山考えたけど……\nそれしか、強くなる道はないと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I’ve thought about it a lot… a lot…\nand I think it’s the only way I can get stronger.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.8193934322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 148.2193934322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "私達で、五人でもっと成長する道を探せないのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can’t we find a way to grow more together‚ as the five of us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.2193934322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "それが出来たら一番だけど……\nでも結局、根本的な解決にならないと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That would be ideal…\nbut I don’t think it’ll solve the fundamental problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8149554879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "それに、みんなには悪いけど\n月ストのみんなといるとどうしても甘えてしまう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I’m sorry to say this to everyone‚ but…\nwhen I’m with everyone in Moon Tempest‚ I can’t help but rely on them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_02-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの優しさに……足を止めてしまう\nだから私は……一人で歩きたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I let their kindness… stop me in my tracks.\nThat’s why I… I want to walk alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.4995856938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
